ly: tombstone beats vanished file. · f=board dormant (Governance docs missing)? Assessments proposals still happen they QUEUE (fleet-governance §5). critical wrong-skill situation queue can't wait unilateral action flagging skill's description UNDER REVIEW (queued proposal <id>)` warning label, edit substance. Content stays untouched. · b:with Other Skills=self-annealing-loop generates intake; skill-quality-audit generates rest., meta's skill-authoring-standards defines what compliant revision looks like; meta's fleet-governance routes proposal., Owning agents stay skill's users; anneal editor, never author-of-record.